<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;">“出操号”声中，青春迷彩方阵整齐列队运动场上。迎着铿锵有力的进行曲，教官队伍精神饱满，整齐跑步入场到达各自的指挥位置。随后全场师生立正肃立，高唱《国歌》、庄重行礼，五星红旗冉冉升起。 9月7日，</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;">江西软件职业技术大学2023级新生军训动员大会在</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;">田径运动场举行。校党委书记、督导专员江延湖，执行校长范红铭等校领导出席大会。各有关职能部门负责人、学院党总支书记和辅导员、教官、本科新生等参加了动员大会。党委副书记、副校长高建国主持了大会。</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28pt; text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28pt;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;"><img src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/img/2023-09-09%2022%3A04%3A550ac005ae477c878008cee16410cad19.jpg?Expires=2009628295&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&Signature=seTjBEwwPbs70%2BXXw6iNWQ0lkfA%3D" alt="" width="650" height="487" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; filter: saturate(1.1); display: block;"/></span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28pt; text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28pt;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;"><img src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/img/2023-09-09%2021%3A58%3A31%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%872.jpg?Expires=2009627911&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&Signature=r6G3RlLJX%2B6ozZ1NE5ywkaQKLlc%3D" alt="" width="650" height="433" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; filter: saturate(1.1); display: block;"/></span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28pt; text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;">动员大会正式开始前，教官组成的示范班为全场人员展示了班队列基本动作，让大家对队列动作有了较全面的了解。教官们精神饱满、动作标准、整齐划一，赢得了全场人员的热烈掌声。</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;">在动员大会上，范红铭以饱满深情作了动员讲话，并代表学校向2023级新生学子表示热烈欢迎。他指出，军训就是进入大学扣的第一粒扣子，军训旨在铸就同学们的强健体魄，提高同学们的思想政治觉悟，激发大家的爱国热情，增强大家的国防观念和国家安全意。希望全体参训人员端正态度，听从指挥；科学组训、文明带训；团结协作，争当模范，在军训中磨练自己、挑战自己、提高自己、完善自己，让青春在历练中闪光，用军训让青春生机勃发！</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28pt; text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28pt;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;"><img src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/img/2023-09-09%2021%3A58%3A51%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%873.png?Expires=2009627931&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&Signature=MPSiCWWgDHI9v5QOh%2FwBoWG4qVk%3D" alt="" width="650" height="461" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; filter: saturate(1.1); display: block;"/></span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28pt; text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;">学工部（处）长邱忠镇宣读了《2023级新生军训工作计划》。教官代表、辅导员代表和新同学代表先后发言。</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;">江延湖用洪亮的声音宣布：“江西软件职业技术大学2023级新生军训开训！”</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28pt; text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28pt;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;"><img src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/img/2023-09-09%2021%3A59%3A09%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%874.png?Expires=2009627949&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&Signature=%2FPbjyG4SC7xqdzxZcJc%2B0JhkSoo%3D" alt="" width="650" height="434" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; filter: saturate(1.1); display: block;"/></span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28pt; text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;">动员大会在雄壮的《中国人民解放军军歌》声中圆满结束。</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28pt; text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28pt;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;"><img src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/img/2023-09-09%2022%3A05%3A23f555c632701adf4f7c842018f8b24d1.jpg?Expires=2009628323&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&Signature=aext8hFbFezrU0sVQtBKJ%2Bvan5I%3D" alt="" width="650" height="487" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; filter: saturate(1.1); display: block;"/></span></p><p><br/></p>